<figureCitation box="[1082,1146,510,531]" captionStart="Figs" captionStartId="3.[197,237,1662,1681]" captionTargetBox="[179,1185,193,1639]" captionTargetId="figure-1@3.[179,1187,192,1639]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="Figs. 1–7. 1–4) Trichohippopsis birai, holotype female: 1) Dorsal habitus; 2) Ventral habitus; 3) Lateral habitus; 4) Head, frontal view; 5) Trichohippopsis exilis, paratype female, dorsal habitus; 6) Trichohippopsis magna, holotype female, dorsal habitus; 7) Trichohippopsis vestita, holotype female, dorsal habitus." pageId="5">Figs. 5</figureCitation>
